{"tid":458273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日一到夜晚就好焦慮","createTime":"2017-11-04T16:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T01:21:29.000Z","uid":85882,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0421941c23fc43e0cef5a1976ca37d02213eee8a","tid":458273,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"唔知出起邊個台好<br />\n我啲朋友話我好陽光好開朗<br />\n得我自己知我唔係<br />\n一臨瞓就會開始自卑<br />\n覺得自己好柒 好on9 好蠢<br />\n做埋啲傻仔野<br />\n好嬲自己 好辛苦 好想尖叫大喊但又唔可以<br />\n每一晚都係咁<br />\n就黎壓力爆<br />\n但第二朝瞓醒又習慣笑住見人 <br />\n好似潛意識話比自己聽唔可以比人知自己脆弱咁<br />\n然後到夜晚又再黎<br />\n我宜家夜晚出post <br />\n我估我聽朝就會後悔po左上黎<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n救命。<br />\n教下我<br />\n我可以點做"},{"pid":"30bec446e193205e8cbe3186ee673053319ddfce","tid":458273,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"賭波啦 即刻咩事都冇<br />\n<br />\n利申輸到仆街"},{"pid":"7e6686c77487cb74a5b7271f30c626fe69afd5ee","tid":458273,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭波啦 即刻咩事都冇<br />\n<br />\n利申輸到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申賭緊"},{"pid":"d5aeac999c2a84f97333e114f8158ffaba9230df","tid":458273,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭波啦 即刻咩事都冇<br />\n<br />\n利申輸到仆街</blockquote><br />\n真係有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd78615223db3547db71c592dca996f09e73dde4","tid":458273,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賭波啦 即刻咩事都冇<br />\n<br />\n利申輸到仆街</blockquote><br />\n真係有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 忘卻晒d煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6af944f27fde54d9909eb98b2a70cb70605a915","tid":458273,"uid":93139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"<bloc